---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Precios" description="Conoce nuestras tarifas de alquiler de scooters eléctricos en el Malecón de Barranquilla">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-dark-blue text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Nuestros Precios</h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">Tarifas accesibles para disfrutar del Malecón de Barranquilla</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Cards Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- 30 min Plan -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <div class="bg-primary py-6 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Plan Básico</h3>
            <p class="text-light-blue">30 minutos</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">$25.000 <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">COP</span></div>
            <ul class="text-left space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Recorrido de 30 minutos
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Scooter eléctrico
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Casco de seguridad
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Instrucciones básicas
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contacto" class="bg-primary text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-secondary transition-colors inline-block">Reservar Ahora</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 40 min Plan -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform scale-105 z-10 border-2 border-primary">
          <div class="bg-secondary py-6 text-center relative">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-accent text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 transform translate-x-2 -translate-y-0 rotate-45 origin-bottom-left">
              POPULAR
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Plan Estándar</h3>
            <p class="text-light-blue">40 minutos</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">$30.000 <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">COP</span></div>
            <ul class="text-left space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Recorrido de 40 minutos
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Scooter eléctrico
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Casco de seguridad
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Instrucciones completas
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contacto" class="bg-secondary text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-primary transition-colors inline-block">Reservar Ahora</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 60 min Plan -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <div class="bg-primary py-6 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Plan Premium</h3>
            <p class="text-light-blue">60 minutos</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">$40.000 <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">COP</span></div>
            <ul class="text-left space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Recorrido de 60 minutos
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Scooter eléctrico premium
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Casco de seguridad
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Guía de puntos de interés
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contacto" class="bg-primary text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-secondary transition-colors inline-block">Reservar Ahora</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Group Pricing Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-light-blue">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Planes Grupales y Corporativos</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Group Plan -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Tours Grupales</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Disfruta de nuestros recorridos en grupo con guía turístico. Perfecto para familias y amigos.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white p-3 rounded-full mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-primary">$40.000 <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">COP por persona</span></span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Grupos de 5-10 personas</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Duración: 1 hora y 30 minutos
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Guía turístico especializado
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Paradas en puntos de interés
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Sesión de fotos incluida
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contacto" class="bg-primary text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-secondary transition-colors inline-block">Solicitar Información</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Corporate Plan -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Eventos Corporativos</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Paquetes personalizados para empresas. Ideal para team building y eventos especiales.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="bg-dark-blue text-white p-3 rounded-full mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-primary">Cotización Personalizada</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Según necesidades y número de participantes</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Actividades de team building
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Personalización con logo de la empresa
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Catering opcional
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Fotografía y video del evento
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contacto" class="bg-dark-blue text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-secondary transition-colors inline-block">Solicitar Cotización</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Preguntas Frecuentes</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">¿Qué incluye el precio del alquiler?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">El precio incluye el alquiler del scooter eléctrico, casco de seguridad, instrucciones básicas de uso y seguro contra accidentes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">¿Necesito experiencia previa para alquilar un scooter?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No es necesario tener experiencia previa. Nuestro personal te dará una breve instrucción sobre cómo manejar el scooter de forma segura.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">¿Cuál es la edad mínima para alquilar?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">La edad mínima para alquilar un scooter es de 12 años. Los menores de 18 años deben estar acompañados por un adulto responsable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">¿Puedo extender el tiempo de alquiler?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Sí, puedes extender el tiempo de alquiler pagando la diferencia correspondiente, siempre que el scooter esté disponible para el período adicional.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">¿Qué métodos de pago aceptan?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Aceptamos efectivo, tarjetas de crédito/débito (Visa, MasterCard, American Express) y transferencias bancarias para reservas anticipadas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-dark-blue text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">¿Listo para vivir la experiencia?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Reserva ahora y disfruta de un recorrido inolvidable por el Malecón de Barranquilla</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contacto" class="bg-white text-primary font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-light-blue transition-colors inline-block">Reservar Ahora</a>
        <a href="/galeria" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors inline-block">Ver Galería</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>